    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091260/extras/f18ee01d9e116e588e8e375940aa20d1.avif?t=1761129525\" width=614 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深夜，你在病房中醒来，不知道过去了多久。抓紧时间逃离这场噩梦。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091260/extras/79fdb811288fd035084c7533b5d56924.avif?t=1761129525\" width=614 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有什么不祥的东西潜伏在黑暗中。赶在被它找到之前尽快脱身。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091260/extras/db02337390ff8b5bc17717643d9ba220.poster.avif?t=1761129525\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091260/extras/db02337390ff8b5bc17717643d9ba220.webm?t=1761129525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091260/extras/db02337390ff8b5bc17717643d9ba220.mp4?t=1761129525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091260/extras/75e6f36e470e8e3b7d84c7acede39726.avif?t=1761129525\" width=614 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集工具，寻找信息，逐步解决谜题并战胜黑暗。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091260/extras/6c1bc1ef61089c0e78bb16f51d551f49.poster.avif?t=1761129525\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091260/extras/6c1bc1ef61089c0e78bb16f51d551f49.webm?t=1761129525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091260/extras/6c1bc1ef61089c0e78bb16f51d551f49.mp4?t=1761129525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091260/extras/4d7699a68d4a8565c701ad38285d3d02.avif?t=1761129525\" width=614 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在医院中帮助生还者，赢取他们的信任，让胜利的天平向你倾斜并逃出生天。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091260/extras/8eae88404e5aa239176c821d4347dd40.poster.avif?t=1761129525\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091260/extras/8eae88404e5aa239176c821d4347dd40.webm?t=1761129525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091260/extras/8eae88404e5aa239176c821d4347dd40.mp4?t=1761129525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
